Package: c4r
Title: Create C4 Architecture Diagrams
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Fabian", "Distler", email = "example@email.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions to create C4 architecture diagrams
    (Context, Container, Component, and Code diagrams) using a simple R
    interface. The package generates diagrams in DOT notation that can be
    rendered using DiagrammeR or other Graphviz-compatible tools.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/fabiandistler/c4r
BugReports: https://github.com/fabiandistler/c4r/issues
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports: 
    cli,
    DiagrammeR,
    dplyr,
    glue,
    purrr,
    rlang,
    stringr,
    tibble
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    spelling,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
